Package: imf.data
Title: An Interface to IMF (International Monetary Fund) Data SDMX 3.0 API
Version: 0.1.7.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Baltazar",, "pedrobtz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple interface to the IMF's new SDMX 3.0 API
    (<https://api.imf.org/external/sdmx/3.0/>). It allows users to search for datasets,
    retrieve metadata, and download data in a user-friendly format.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
